00:26:19.590 --> 00:26:26.810
On January 6th, 1941, President
Franklin Delano Roosevelt stood

00:26:26.810 --> 00:26:30.770
before a joint session of congress
to deliver his annual State

00:26:30.770 --> 00:26:35.570
of the Union address in that
speech Roosevelt argued for an end

00:26:35.570 --> 00:26:39.300
